1. *Stani* pa se malo odmori. (Stop and rest a little.)
2. On je *stanio* da se ne umori. (He stopped so he doesn't get tired.)
3. *Stani* da vidimo šta ćemo dalje. (Stop so we can see what to do next.)
4. Oni su *stanuli* kad su čuli zvuk. (They stopped when they heard the sound.)
5. *Stani* pa pogledaj bolje. (Stop and look better.)
6. Oni su *stanovali* ovde nekoliko godina. (They lived here for few years.)